description:
&lt;p&gt;At the East of England Ambulance Service Trust we have a dedicated employment relations team who are committed to providing the best possible care for our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To achieve this we are seeking highly experienced employment relations investigating officers to join the Trust’s Bank team, who can be called upon to undertake highly complex investigations on an ad-hoc basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidates will have a proven track record on undertaking complex investigations within an NHS environment, which may include Maintaining High Professional Standards. It is also essential to have experience at presenting investigation reports at formal hearings and being cross examined.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameKaren CarterJob titleHead of HREmail addresskaren.carter@eastamb.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
